==經濟和旅遊業==
[[File:Road_leading_to_Shushi.JPG|thumb]]
當該鎮在亞美尼亞人的控制之下，舒沙復興基金——ArmeniaFund——以及[[阿爾察赫共和國|阿爾察赫共和國]]政府正在努力振興該市的經濟。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.shushi.org/en/index.php |title=Archived copy |access-date=2012-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121222165657/http://www.shushi.org/en/index.php |archive-date=2012-12-22 |url-status=live }}</ref>對旅遊業的投資促成了Shushi Hotel、Avan Shushi Plaza Hotel和Shushi Grand Hotel的開業。還開設了一個旅遊信息辦公室，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.shushi.org/prog_proj_new.php |title=Archived copy |access-date=2012-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111009025349/http://www.shushi.org/prog_proj_new.php |archive-date=2011-10-09 |url-status=live }}</ref>這是[[阿爾察赫共和國|阿爾察赫共和國]]的第一個。剩下兩座亞美尼亞教堂（[[聖救主主教座堂_(舒沙)|聖救主主教座堂]]和{{le|施洗者聖約翰教堂|Kanach Zham}}）得到翻新，學校、博物館，以及Naregatsi艺术学院（Naregatsi Art Institute）都開辦了。

奪回該鎮後，阿塞拜疆當局翻新並開辦了Khari Bulbul酒店<ref>{{cite news |title=Official web-site of Presidentof Azerbaijan Republic |url=https://en.president.az/articles/51467 |access-date=2021-11-04 |agency=en.president.az |date=2021-05-12 |language=en}}</ref>和Karabakh酒店。<ref>{{cite news |title=President Ilham Aliyev and First Lady Mehriban Aliyeva attended inauguration of "Qarabag" hotel in Shusha |url=https://azertag.az/en/xeber/President_Ilham_Aliyev_and_First_Lady_Mehriban_Aliyeva_attended_inauguration_of_Qarabag_hotel_in_Shusha_VIDEO-1863603 |access-date=2021-11-04 |agency=AZERTAC |date=2021-08-29 |language=en}}</ref>2021年8月，阿塞拜疆總統伊利哈姆·阿利耶夫為舒沙酒店及會議中心奠基。<ref>{{cite news |title=President Ilham Aliyev laid foundation stone for Hotel and Conference Center in Shusha |url=https://apa.az/en/xeber/official-news/president-ilham-aliyev-laid-foundation-stone-for-hotel-and-conference-center-in-shusha-356724 |access-date=2021-11-04 |work=Apa.az |agency=Apa.az |language=en}}</ref>

